🚀 Introducing the AI Powered Movie Recommender! 🎬✨
Discover Your Next Cinematic Obsession 🎥

Tired of scrolling through endless movie lists? Our innovative app is here to revolutionize your film-watching experience. Say goodbye to generic recommendations and hello to personalized movie suggestions tailored to your unique taste. 🍿

An advanced Movie Recommedation System, which not just suggest movies, but also dives detailed insights, from captivating plot summaries to behind-the-scenes trivia, to the suggest movies, to building curiosity for the movie adventure  🎥🍿🌟
Your next movie is a one button ahead, find it 🎬✨

Tools and Libraries:
1. autogen
2. LM Studios
3. Streamlit
4. Zephyr Beta 7B llm
5. Content based movie recommendation
6. OMDB API
7. hugging face models


Data Collection:
1. https://www.kaggle.com/code/rounakbanik/movie-recommender-systems
2. OMDB 


